The paper discusses hardware security for electronic systems and integrated circuits, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also mentions electronic design automation (EDA), which is related to embedded systems (cs.ET) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper discusses the synthesis of countermeasures, which is related to computer architecture (cs.AR) and control systems (cs.SY).
